# Claude Code worktrees (sub-agents create these; not part of the repo)
.claude/

# F-D11-11: defense-in-depth against `gyt add .` accidentally
# staging operator key material. None of these should ever live in
# a tracked file, but mistakes happen and these patterns catch the
# common shapes.
*.pem
*.key
id_ed25519
id_ed25519.pub
id_ed25519_*
ci-key
*.tls-ticket-key
